reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars After almost a year
reviews.reviewText: After taking these vitamins for almost a year, I can say they are great and do work really well. My hair has always grown rather quickly, but I does seem much healthy. My nails grow very quickly and extremely long, but since taking these vitamins my nails are growing in strong! Even with them being very long they don’t break as easily as they would normally tend to do. As far as skin benefits I think I will need to take these vitamins longer to actually tell. Nonetheless, we start losing the amount of collagen our body produces naturally around early-mid twenties, so taking high dosages daily will of course help with keeping your skin from aging as quickly. All in all these have been wonderful vitamins which I will continue to take.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Heartburn - Formula Change?
reviews.reviewText: The first bottle I purchased in Sept 2023, was great. It did give me heartburn so like others, I opened the capsules and dissolved them in my morning coffee. It dissolved well, like a coffee creamer does and the heartburn issue resolved and my hair started filling in at the temples. I was thrilled. I ordered the two pack and started the second bottle, but it appears the formula has changed. The powder clumps up in hard lumps, in my coffee and does not dissolve. I get severe heartburn if I take the capsules, and severe heartburn if I open them and try to mix them with my coffee. I will be looking for another brand that dissolves better.

I am on my one week now with this product and I can already see improvements on my skin, hair and nails. Surprisingly, my joints and muscle feel stronger when I run on my treadmill. By the way, Im already 48 years old .
This is the first time I purchased this product. I love it! It helps clear the few pimples on my face and makes my skin better. I highly recommend it!
